             was indicted for <rs id="t18201206-61-off384" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18201206-61-off384" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18201206-61-off384" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18201206-61-cd385" type="crimeDate">7th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-61-off384 t18201206-61-cd385"></join>, one handkerchief, value 6 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18201206-61-victim625" type="victimName">
                           Francis Neat 
                           Walsh
                        <interp inst="t18201206-61-victim625" type="surname" value="Walsh"></interp>
